column2: b'Re:Zero kara Hajimeru Isekai Seikatsu - Memory Snow - Manner Movie'

b'A manner movie shown before Re:Zero kara Hajimeru Isekai Seikatsu - Memory Snow. It features the cast in chibi form speaking to the viewer asking them to behave such as by turning off cellphones and to avoid smoking inside the theater.'
[b'Re:Zero kara Hajimeru Isekai Seikatsu', b'Re:Zero kara Hajimeru Isekai Seikatsu - Memory Snow']
